msgstr ""
"对于Windows用户，在Windows上部署MongoDB时可以参考 `Windows Server Technet "
"Article on TCP Configuration <http://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/"
"dd349797.aspx>`_。"

#: ../source/administration/production-notes.txt:217
